en_8886641_0	Two foreign currency exchange centres that were operating in Galle without permission from the Central Bank of Sri Lanka were raided.
en_8886641_1	Seven suspects have been arrested.
en_8886641_2	Police stated that the suspects were remanded until July 14, after they were produced before the Galle Magistrate’s Court.
en_8886641_3	The Criminal Investigation Department had begun investigations into illegal foreign currency exchange centres that were operating in Galle, based on a tip-off received.
en_8886641_4	Police said that during the investigations, two such exchange centre were raided and seven suspects were arrested.
en_8886641_5	The suspects arrested are residents of Galle.The CID have begun further investigations into the matter.
